---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SchemaMarkup from "../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro";
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";

// Make this page dynamic via SSR
export const prerender = false;

const publishDate = new Date("September 21 2026");
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

// FAQ Schema data for AEO optimization
const faqSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  mainEntity: []
};
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Is a First-Time Deep Clean Necessary Before Routine Service? | The Valley Clean Team"
  description="Why do cleaning companies require an initial deep clean? Learn why a first-time deep clean is essential for establishing a baseline for routine service."
  ogImage="https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/iKQIBhpKVL2XVPgU7HMd/media/6920802945dc047d65b4ec5d.png"
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="Is a First-Time Deep Clean Necessary Before Routine Service?"
    description="Why do cleaning companies require an initial deep clean? Learn why a first-time deep clean is essential for establishing a baseline for routine service."
    publishDate="September 21 2026"
    author={author}
  />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          FAQ/Conversion
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Is a First-Time Deep Clean Necessary Before Routine Service?
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming September 21 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>September 21 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <!-- TODO: REPLACE THIS SECTION WITH YOUR ACTUAL BLOG CONTENT -->
          <h2>Is a First-Time Deep Clean Necessary Before Routine Service?</h2>
<p><strong>Yes, a first-time deep clean is often necessary before starting routine cleaning services. This initial comprehensive clean ensures that your home meets the high standards required for efficient and effective ongoing maintenance. In The Shoals & Surrounding Areas, this approach guarantees a consistent, detailed clean with each service thereafter.</strong></p>

<h3>Why Start with a First-Time Deep Clean?</h3>
<p>A first-time deep clean sets the stage for streamlined, consistent upkeep. This meticulous process allows our trained cleaning specialists to address every corner of your home, establishing a baseline that makes routine maintenance more effective and time-efficient.</p>

<h4>What Does a First-Time Deep Clean Involve?</h4>
<p>Our deep clean goes beyond the surface. Here's what you can expect:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Comprehensive Dusting:</strong> We tackle everything from ceiling fans to baseboards.</li>
  <li><strong>Detailed Kitchen Cleaning:</strong> Appliances, cabinets, and countertops are not just wiped but thoroughly cleaned.</li>
  <li><strong>Bathroom Scrubbing:</strong> Tiles, grout, fixtures—cleaned with precision and care.</li>
  <li><strong>Floor Care:</strong> Vacuuming, mopping, and specific treatments for different flooring types.</li>
</ul>

<p>This process transforms your space, making routine visits more efficient and cost-effective.</p>

<h3>The Benefits of a Deep Clean in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas</h3>
<p>The Shoals & Surrounding Areas are known for their unique climate, which can bring specific cleaning challenges. A first-time deep clean addresses these issues head-on, from humidity-induced mold to pollen accumulation, ensuring your home is a healthy, inviting space.</p>

<h4>Investing in Quality and Longevity</h4>
<p>By starting with a deep clean, you invest in the longevity of your home's surfaces and finishes. Our specialists use premium products and techniques that protect your investments and maintain the beauty of your home for the long term.</p>

<h3>Transitioning to Routine Service</h3>
<p>Once your home is thoroughly deep cleaned, transitioning to routine service becomes seamless. Our military-precision checklists ensure that each visit maintains the standard set by the initial deep clean, focusing on:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Consistency:</strong> Every cleaning session is thorough and meets our strict standards.</li>
  <li><strong>Efficiency:</strong> With a clean slate, routine services are quicker, keeping costs down.</li>
  <li><strong>Tailored Approach:</strong> We adapt to your home's specific needs over time, ensuring optimal results.</li>
</ul>

<p>Our systematic approach guarantees that your home remains in peak condition, reflecting the care and quality The Valley Clean Team is known for.</p>

<h3>Ready for a Spotless Home? Book Your First-Time Deep Clean Today!</h3>
<p>Reclaim your time and enjoy a pristine home environment starting with a thorough deep clean by The Valley Clean Team. Our specialists are ready to deliver guaranteed, military-precision results that set the standard for all future cleanings. Book your first-time deep clean in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas now and experience the difference. Get your free quote and see availability—schedule your guaranteed service today!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">September 21 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )}
</BaseLayout>
